<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV62">
<l>karaṇṭamāṭu poykaiyuṭka rumpaṉaippe rumpaḻam</l>
<l>puraṇṭuvīḻa vāḷaipāyku ṟuṅkuṭine ṭuntakāy</l>
<l>tiraṇṭatōḷi raṇiyaṉci ṉaṅkoḷāka moṉṟaiyu</l>
<l>miraṇṭukūṟu ceytukanta ciṅkameṉpa tuṉṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O worthy [Lord] from Kuṟuṅkuṭi where big, black palm fruits slip off and fall</l>
<l>into the pond in which coots play and the scabbard fish leap!</l>
<l>Is it You who are said to be the lion that rejoiced splitting into two slices</l>
<l>The angry, matchless chest of Hiraṇya[kaśipu] with bulging arms?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
